description: If my angel number is 222, thats 2+2+2=6. I am 24 now so thats 2+4 =6. 6+6=12, 12 is half of 24. I guess at this point I am just doing math. But technically isn't this my 25 year on the earth? At what point does the age you are stop making sense? Idk catch you on the flip side
